        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Hrett, your diagram shows the levels expanding a bit after 54, for the after picture.  All levels from 51-60 are extended, there is no magic 54 multiplier anymore.  Each level after 51 will need more exp, but if you fight the appropriate mobs, you will need the same amount of each mob to level up to 60.  At 58 say you fight level 45 mobs, then at 59 you need to fight level 46 mobs for instance to gain a level with the same number of mobs.    </P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
