         It is faster to level overall now though in single groups hunting L50+ mobs rather than grinding on low blues in places like velks.  Like Daedrea said, 57 and 58 are noticeably slower though.</P><P>Mobs L50+ give more exp the higher they are.  For example, ever done a single group arena armor grind in the past?  Exp sucked right?  Not anymore.  I was making respectable exp in a 5 person arena group clearing the arena just for faction and armor.</P><P>Ssra exp was damn nice.  CT?  Uuuuuuuunreal.</P><P>So you will be able to level faster now than ever before if these changes go live.</P><P>But I don't think it's because they want a bunch of L60's (already more reaching L60 than we lose to attrition).  I think its because the level cap will raise again and L61+ players will need to kill L55+ mobs just to level then.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
